text.section:
The State Property and Buildings Commission, in each resolution authorizing the issuance of revenue bonds under the provisions of KRS 40.330 and this section, shall determine the following:
The maturity date or dates of the revenue bonds;
The manner in which interest shall be paid thereon;
The terms of redemption applicable thereto; and
Such other particulars of the revenue bonds not contrary to law or inconsistent with KRS 40.330 and this section.
